# Musik KITA Domain-Aware Development

> author: Musik KITA | version: 2.0

## Golden Rule

**Saat menjawab pertanyaan fitur, flow, atau lokasi kode:**

1. **DOMAIN dulu** — business logic, rules, flows
2. **CODE kemudian** — filePath dari steps, entity mapping
3. **Jangan load file penuh** — pakai graph references + targeted lookup

**Urutan lookup:** domain graph (ini) → knowledge graph (`musik-kita-knowledge-graph.mdc`) → snippet kode spesifik.

## Domain References

@.understand-anything/reference-domain-index.json

**7 domain:** Student Lifecycle · Penjadwalan & Absensi · Billing & Payments · Honor Guru · Event · Master Data · Laporan & Notifikasi

